description: Enhancing the Institutional Capacity of the Presidency of the Republic of Lebanon

subproject.corporate outcome: National and local institutions have the capacity to deliver improved justice and security, including safeguarding citizen security, in conflict-affected settings
subproject.description:
Professional support, knowledge, resources and advice provided to the responsible entities and related public institutions upon their request and within the framework of the objectives of this project.

Technical assistance, essential resources and professional support provided to develop and strengthen the mechanisms, initiatives and structures to sustain civil peace
